# --- System Trash ---
# These are hidden files Windows and Mac create that look messy on GitHub
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Editor Settings ---
# This hides your personal VS Code or text editor settings
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.scratch

# --- Logs ---
# If your code ever crashes and makes an error log, this keeps it private
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# --- Personal Notes ---
# This is the "Secret Sauce" line. 
# Anything you put in a file called 'notes.txt' will stay on your 
# computer and NEVER be seen on GitHub. 
# Use this to keep track of your inspiration safely!
notes.txt
